WEBVTT

00:00:01.180 --> 00:00:03.095
I'm quite comfortable sitting here.

00:00:03.851 --> 00:00:05.002
Don't get me wrong,

00:00:05.026 --> 00:00:08.010
my heart's beating so loud
I'm surprised you can't hear it.

00:00:08.512 --> 00:00:10.483
There's a lightness in my head,

00:00:10.507 --> 00:00:12.521
and my hand is a little sweaty.

00:00:13.615 --> 00:00:17.670
Luckily, I'm not only familiar
with these sensations --

00:00:17.694 --> 00:00:18.844
I enjoy them.

00:00:21.659 --> 00:00:25.347
(Music)

00:00:25.371 --> 00:00:27.284
Over my career as an aerialist,

00:00:27.308 --> 00:00:30.263
I've learned to listen
to those signs from my body,